OL,3,CLoyalist Irvine jailed but 'peace'
OL,4,Cefforts see him escape five-year term
OL,6,FIrvine's co-accused in the case, Robin
OL,7,FWorkman, was handed the statutory five-
OL,8,Fyear sentence by Judge Kerr.
OL,10,FHe will also serve half of that term
OL,11,Fbehind bars.
OL,13,FIrvine, 49, of Ballysillan Road in
OL,14,Fnorth Belfast and Workman, 54, of
OL,15,FShore Road in Larne, County Antrim had
OL,16,Fboth previously admitted possession of
OL,17,Fa firearm and ammunition in suspicious
OL,18,Fcircumstances.
