OL,3,CLoyalist Irvine jailed but 'peace'
OL,4,Cefforts see him escape five-year term
OL,6,FWhile the judge noted that UVF
OL,7,Fparaphernalia was found in the homes
OL,8,Fof both defendants he did not consider
OL,9,Fthere was a terrorist link to the
OL,10,Fweapons that were seized.
OL,12,FSeveral references crediting Irvine
OL,13,Ffor peacebuilding work in Northern
OL,14,FIreland were submitted by his legal
OL,15,Fteam, including from David Campbell,
OL,16,Fchairman of the Loyalist Communities
OL,17,FCouncil (LCC), and former Northern
OL,18,FIreland Policing Board member Debbie
OL,19,FWatters.
