OL,6,FThe judge added: "My finding does not,
OL,7,Fhowever, mean that I should ignore the
OL,8,Fpurpose behind that provision in
OL,9,Fdeterring such offences by the
OL,10,Fimposition of custodial sentencing,
OL,11,Fbut such sentence should reflect the
OL,12,Fdefendant's circumstances and allow
OL,13,Ffor appropriate mitigation."
